Job Description
If you want to learn and do something new every day - this is the right job for you!We provide Virtual Personal and Administrative Assistance to clients throughout the world. Most of the work is research work.We are looking for people who are fluent in English (verbal & written). Have excellent communication skills. Self-motivated, keen learners and willing to work long-term. We are doing something new every hour so you must be up for challenges with the ability to think out of the box.Looking for fresh candidates for Night Shift (11PM-7AM).*Please do not apply if you can not work in the night shift.95% of the work is research, rest is mostly administrative work and includes but not limited to:- Data Mining- Email management- Calendar management- Social media management- Travel planning & arrangements Please note *THIS IS NOT A CALL CENTER JOB, WE DO NOT SELL OR MARKET ANYTHING.*
Job Specification
Below is what we are looking for in the applicants:Excellent written and spoken English!Familiarity with: - Google Search Engine - Gmail - Internet concepts - Web Apps
